{
  "stem": "15540.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my father had made, had had some small ladders made that-- so that the-- grown-ups could climb over the ladders at night when there was curfew and spend the evenings together.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So there was a real network in this little enclave.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And these were friends, and we stayed with them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, not-- the, the ladders had nothing to do with that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was, had to do with the curfew in general, and that if they wanted to see each other, you know, and get together socially at night, this was the only way they could do it.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "These were, were friends who were not Jewish.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, I mean, the-- I know all my, my family and friends and everybody was sheltering somebody.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And a lot of people knew people who had summer houses, and they fled out to the country and stayed in, in their friends' summer houses out in the country.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So everybody was opening their, their homes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, there had been-- the communication had been between the, the head of the Jewish community and, and-- who had constantly been in, in touch with the ministry and had kept telling them nothing was happening.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But on that day, I believe it was, there was a German man who was involved with the Ministry of Commerce, and he went to the ministry and told them that this was happening.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Everybody, just about everybody, went into hiding, and very fast.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there was a lot of bicycling around town to, to, to warn people, because of course you didn't want to talk on the phone.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Nothing was, was safe in that respect.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So everybody was bicycling around town, telling everybody else to hide.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
